<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.6">
<l>vammiṉ pulavīrnum meyvarut tikkaicey tuymmiṉō</l>
<l>vimmaṉ ṉulakil celvarip pōtillai nōkkiṉō</l>
<l>nummiṉ kavikoṇṭu nunumiṭ ṭāteyva mēttiṉāl</l>
<l>cemmiṉ cuṭarmuṭi yeṉṟiru mālukku cērumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, you poets. Escape by making your bodies suffer [and] woking with [your] hands.</l>
<l>In this lasting world there are no rich people. We are people who have seen [that].</l>
<l>If you take your pleasing poems [and] praise the deity as the one chosen by each of you,</l>
<l>it will reach my Tirumāl with a red flashing glowing crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
